aning of his name is unclear. If he is mentioned at all by his contemporary monarchs against whom he would have fought it is only obliquely or only intimated by omissions or partial spellings in context. This volume attempts to advance scholarship addressing these concerns.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / Old Testament.2bisacsh1 aCaspi, Mishael M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaspi, Mishael M., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEllens, J. Harold, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreene, John T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreene, John T., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPeleg, Yitzhak, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aReisenberger, Azila, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSherwin, Richard E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSong, Angeline M. G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSpunaugle, Adrianne L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStern, Max, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTan, Nancy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2015z978311066303708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertReligious Studies Gorgias eBook Packagez978311071684940uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146323523940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463235239423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463235239/original  a978-3-11-066303-7  Gorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2